    <string name="slide_5_title">Step Detection</string>
    <string name="slide_5_desc">The app detects your steps based on different algorithms. On some devices you can define the sensivity of step detection in settings. In addition to that you can add steps you walked without the app or correct the stepcount on daily activity chart.</string>
    <string name="slide_3_desc">Define custom walking modes and notifications if the achievement of your daily step goal is in danger.</string>
